2004-02-04  Jody Goldberg <jody@gnome.org>

	* Release 1.2.6

2004-02-04  Jody Goldberg <jody@gnome.org>

	* graph/gog-legend.c (gog_legend_editor) : new to avoid warning.

	* graph/plugins/plot_pie/gog-pie.c (gog_pie_plot_foreach_elem) :
	  handle insufficient labels more smoothly.

