	http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=132390
	* graph/gog-style.c (cb_fg_color_changed) : set_style frees the new
	  style do not attempt to use it.
	(cb_bg_color_changed) : ditto.
	(cb_fill_gradient_start_color) : ditto.
	(cb_fill_gradient_end_color) : ditto.
	(cb_marker_outline_color_changed) : ditto.
	(cb_marker_fill_color_changed) : ditto.

